I have been hearing Pakistani music for some time now (read as 'few weeks') and I really admire their music, arts and culture. I was introduced to Coke Studio a few days back, and I wondered why I hadn't heard of it before. I have been listening to all Coke Studio songs on loop now.The music is bliss and all I can say is keep up the good work! 
Love, from across the border. :)
